{"data":[{"name":"107:1","price":"1. Heb je degenen gezien die de afrekening ontkent?","arabic":"أَرَءَيۡتَ ٱلَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِٱلدِّينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6198,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"107:2","price":"2. Dat is degenen die (meedogenloos) de wees afstoot.","arabic":"فَذَٰلِكَ ٱلَّذِي يَدُعُّ ٱلۡيَتِيمَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6199,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"107:3","price":"3. En niet (zichzelf noch anderen) aanspoort tot het voeden van de armen.","arabic":"وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَىٰ طَعَامِ ٱلۡمِسۡكِينِ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6200,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"107:4","price":"4. O wee, voor diegenen die (onachtzaam) in hun gebeden.","arabic":"فَوَيۡلٞ لِّلۡمُصَلِّينَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6201,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"107:5","price":"5. Die hun gebeden uitstellen van hun bepaalde tijd.","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَن صَلَاتِهِمۡ سَاهُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6202,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"107:6","price":"6. Degenen die slechts goed doen om gezien te worden (in gebed e.a.).","arabic":"ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ يُرَآءُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6203,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"},{"name":"107:7","price":"7. En de levensnoodzakelijke benodigdheden weigeren.","arabic":"وَيَمۡنَعُونَ ٱلۡمَاعُونَ","category":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un"],"ayahNumber":6204,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"nl"}],"chapter":["107 (Al-Ma'un)","Al-Ma'un","Surah Al-Ma'un","Chapter Al-Ma'un","Ma'un","Surah Ma'un","Chapter Ma'un","Al Ma'un","Surah Al Ma'un","Chapter Al Ma'un","Surah 107","Chapter 107","The Small Kindnesses","الماعون"]}